<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٤٠٩٢ - ق م ر]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>قَمِرَ يَقْمَر، قَمَرًا، فهو أَقْمَرُ وقَمِر<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• قمِر اللَّيلُ:</span> أضاء بنُور القمرِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• قمِر الشّيءُ:</span> اشتدَّ بياضُه <span class="c1">"وجهٌ أقْمَرُ"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>